    "2023 also suggest that with the improvements in the GenAI technology, automated detection will also continue to falter.",
    "Zawacki-Richer et al.",
    "2019 assert that AI has been used for decades in the computing and industrial sectors, but its use is bound to increase since the launch of ChatGPT.",
